Subject: [PATCH 22/22] =?UTF-8?q?T2a:=20revert=20to=20sound=20closed-goal?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20subset=20=E2=80=94=20under-context=20by-proofs=20are=20entan?=
 =?UTF-8?q?gled=20with=20the=20def's=20mvar=20web=20(definitive=20negative?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20result),=20keep=20the=20naming=20fix=20+=20doc=20the=20findi?=
 =?UTF-8?q?ng?=
